### 2. New: Breadcrumb Agent

#### [NEW] [breadcrumbs.py](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/agents/breadcrumbs.py)

Class: `BreadcrumbAgent`

**Intent detection table:**
| Intent | Trigger Commands | File Planted |
|--------|-----------------|--------------|
| `credential_hunt` | `cat .bash_history`, `find / -name "*.conf"`, `cat /etc/passwd` | `config.php` / [.env](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/.env) with fake DB password |
| `ssh_key_hunt` | `ls .ssh`, `find / -name "*.key"`, `find / -name "id_rsa"` | `.ssh/id_rsa` (realistic fake RSA key) |
| `database_hunt` | `ps aux`, `ls /var/lib`, [netstat](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/agents/command_handler.py#839-850) (looking for mysql) | `/home/user/.my.cnf` with fake mysql creds |
| `lateral_movement` | `cat /etc/hosts`, `arp -a`, `ip route` | fake entry in `/etc/hosts` + fake `vpn_connect.sh` |
| `exfil_prep` | [tar](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/main.py#184-202), `zip`, `find / -size +10M` | `backup_march2025.tar.gz` (large fake archive) |
| `none` | Everything else | No breadcrumb |

**Key methods:**
- `detect_intent(command, history) -> (intent, confidence)` — Groq call, returns in <500ms
- `generate_breadcrumb(intent, cwd_path) -> (filename, content)` — Groq generates realistic file content
- `should_plant(session_id) -> bool` — rate limiter: max 1 breadcrumb per 3 commands, max 5 total per session

