### 3. Command Handler

#### [MODIFY] [command_handler.py](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/agents/command_handler.py)

In [_cmd_cat()](file:///d:/just%20learning/ghostnet/agents/command_handler.py#371-388) — after reading the file, check if it's a canary:
